{"tid":2344698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港英烈] Captain Ansari ：與其苟且悔恨一生，不如英勇就義","createTime":"2020-12-29T03:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T02:01:49.000Z","uid":43150,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"68f5e63d47e69c258ebf3b275f686082bd047f10","tid":2344698,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/87738069_1098952517106182_4013353707809800192_o-1-627x627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F87738069_1098952517106182_4013353707809800192_o-1-627x627.jpg&h=9670e584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//1941年12月香港保衛戰期間，守軍主力有英屬印度陸軍的第7拉吉普團第5營（5/7th Rajput Regiment）和第14#旁遮普團第2營（2/14th Punjab Regiment）。兩營印度兵與日軍作戰英勇，蒙受重大傷亡，拉吉普營更是此次戰役傷亡最慘重的部隊。拉吉普營先是陣守醉酒灣防線東翼，繼而在魔鬼山奮戰為「大陸旅」撤回港島殿後，其後再在北角首當其衝抵擋日軍登陸總攻擊。此役，共有892人的<strong>拉吉普營有156人戰死、113 人下落不明、193人受傷，傷亡率達51%。當中，全數17名軍官戰死或負傷。</strong><br />\n<br />\n安薩里上尉 Captain Mateen Ahmed Ansari（1916-1943）隸屬拉吉普營A連，香港淪陷後，他被關進為印度兵而設的馬頭涌戰俘營（Ma Tau Chung POW Camp）。安薩里是伊斯蘭教徒，出身印度名門望族之家，受訓於著名的桑赫斯特皇家軍事學院（Royal Military Academy Sandhurst）。由於地位崇高，日軍曾企圖攏絡他帶領印兵變節，為日軍服務，但安薩里斷言拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n1942年1月，賴廉士上校（Sir Lindsay Tasman Ride）成功逃出香港後，成立英軍服務團（British Army Aids Group）營救在港戰俘。<strong>儘管面對死亡威脅，安薩里仍然按照英軍服務團的指引，秘密與深水埗、亞皆老街戰俘營的英軍軍官聯絡，策劃一場大型逃脫行動</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n1943年4月16日，安薩里透過印度籍特工高禮和（Naranjan Singh Grewal），向英軍服務團總部傳達了一道加密訊息，表示自己雖受日軍嚴刑迫供，但現已康復，隨時可以實行逃脫行動。<br />\n<br />\n可惜現實並不如電影般完美，邪未必不能勝正。就在四日前，4月12日，特工兼前 香港義勇防衛軍第三連成員葛德麟（George Kotwall），被叛徒出賣，繼而被日軍憲兵隊拘捕並處死，逃脫行動因而敗露。同年5月，安薩里被捕，被帶到赤柱拘留營，慘受饑餓之苦及被憲兵虐打。然而，<strong>安薩里苦撐至10月仍然守口如瓶，沒有供出任何對英軍不利的情報。</strong><br />\n<br />\n1943年10月29日，日軍似乎失去耐性，<strong>安薩里、高禮和一共30名英、印、華籍英軍服務團特工及相關人士都被處以斬首之刑。</strong>行刑前，安薩里展現出最後的忠誠和勇氣，根據其他生還者憶述，他當時仍然安慰身邊的人：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Everybody has to die sometime. Many die daily from disease, some suffer painful, lingering deaths. We will die strong and healthy for an ideal; not as traitors, but nobly in our country&rsquo;s cause. We cannot now escape the enemy&rsquo;s sword, but no one should give in to years or regrets, but instead face the enemy with a smile and die bravely.&rdquo;<strong><span class=\"x-large\">「人終需一死，很多人因病離世，承受揮之不去的痛楚。我們會堅強而健康地死去，全為信念，不作叛徒，高貴地為國捐軀。我們如今避不過敵人的劍了，但無人應流淚或抱憾，我們要含笑面對敵人，勇敢地命赴黃泉。」</span></strong>//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111add4ca5b087c6acc04beb2e524b998e488ebe","tid":2344698,"uid":43150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/%e5%ae%89%e8%96%a9%e9%87%8c%e4%b8%8a%e5%b0%89%ef%bc%9a%e5%af%a7%e6%ad%bb%e4%b8%8d%e5%b1%88%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%9b%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%b0%e5%85%b5%e8%bb%8d%e5%ae%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2F%25e5%25ae%2589%25e8%2596%25a9%25e9%2587%258c%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%25b0%2589%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25af%25a7%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25b1%2588%25e7%259a%2584%25e8%25a1%259b%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258d%25b0%25e5%2585%25b5%25e8%25bb%258d%25e5%25ae%2598%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzxxs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=48f1aef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com/%e5%ae%89%e8%96%a9%e9%87%8c%e4%b8%8a%e5%b0%89%ef%bc%9a%e5%af%a7%e6%ad%bb%e4%b8%8d%e5%b1%88%e7%9a%84%e8%a1%9b%e6%b8%af%e5%8d%b0%e5%85%b5%e8%bb%8d%e5%ae%98/</a>"},{"pid":"28ff6991fed1d71c2f1e1ecc8a890c487fa47001","tid":2344698,"uid":91771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:27:52.000Z","msg":"真係要搵日去赤柱墳場悼念....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd45073d54c332b38e08e9a1dd8560c66aa8af41","tid":2344698,"uid":105738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639a0abfc943c5475ab62fac3e6e90a2e12bc70c","tid":2344698,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82faf08778c23f391a717b09bf32383b55da5d5a","tid":2344698,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"Salute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202cb57a6e72d75d257f8b2e227c015b4e8582e9","tid":2344698,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"南亞手足"},{"pid":"c528d9c97db2703391483b7497914c6b2e6ed335","tid":2344698,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"香港人：做乜咁蠢送頭，鬥長命先有智慧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e331f402051e8c17f326cb950748980bf853b086","tid":2344698,"uid":42064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實真係好癲<br />\n印度人，自己本身已經係俾人殖民，又唔係守印度，又唔係守英國，只係幫緊宗主國另一d𡃁，都肯搏命"},{"pid":"f7849901ec3446983be0d9a661ae81fe207e94b2","tid":2344698,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"南亞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef623fa07f6f3663c43e54add64224e68b65271f","tid":2344698,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b177b26ee0dbf68cdffd47ba3aa105ffcc1c88ea","tid":2344698,"uid":132399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"tears and regret"},{"pid":"1f33ca553712a57ab339dfdfe8de3cc9f70fb004","tid":2344698,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"香港華人唔識咁諗"},{"pid":"46d1c650e4fb621c0443b6d7506932dc3f2b881b","tid":2344698,"uid":132256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"我都想有佢嘅勇氣"},{"pid":"adaf92bf8e49b2170630ae19ae21e3435b26f61c","tid":2344698,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d1c650e4fb621c0443b6d7506932dc3f2b881b","tid":2344698,"uid":132256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"我都想有佢嘅勇氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65052614d33aa6c3578700e2307e160f0b9258fa","tid":2344698,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"如果俾国安捉咗可能都要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450c89a10e78a5b4ac6cf292eefb4fe1d8682b6e","tid":2344698,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3553446626c41189a99ce92c4a7fa01e24565fa4","tid":2344698,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65052614d33aa6c3578700e2307e160f0b9258fa","tid":2344698,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"如果俾国安捉咗可能都要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"澳洲定NZ華人雷福榮就係俾人捉到而壯烈成仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢暗中幫BAAG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//日軍反間諜行動<br />\n1943年春，日本憲兵隊展開行動，打擊地下抵抗活動。是年3月，位於沙頭角的中共據點遭到突襲，而國軍特務人員的秘密基地亦遭破獲。<br />\n<br />\n日軍亦曾以運送金錢到赤柱拘留營為名，拘捕司徒永覺醫生；及後又因此案拘捕數名銀行家及醫護人員。日軍懷疑司徒永覺是英軍在港情報系統的首領；被捕者還包括匯豐銀行大班祈禮賓，他最終因為遭受酷刑及營養不良，在赤柱監獄離世。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行大班祈禮賓<br />\n1943年4月，日本憲兵隊又成功滲透英軍服務團及戰俘營之間的聯繫網絡。是時，印度獨立聯盟成員冒充印軍軍官安沙里上尉，誘使英軍服務團情報人員暴露身份，並使安沙里因此被捕。砵蘭街的Z站亦被日軍破獲。同年5月，「C組」有成員背叛，數名人員被捕，當中包括一名貨車司機，他一直負責為戰俘送遞訊息。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日，日軍又逼令一名和英軍服務團合作的司機在亞皆老街戰俘營向戰俘傳遞假訊息。日軍計謀得逞以後，亞皆老街及深水埗戰俘營內官兵數人被捕。7月10日，紐臨上校被捕。<br />\n<br />\n同日被日本憲兵隊拘捕者，還包括霍德上尉、皇家空軍的加利中尉，以及身處深水埗戰俘營的皇家加拿大通訊軍團萊歷治中士。至此，戰俘營地下抵抗活動的中堅份子大多被捕。<br />\n<br />\n日軍亦破獲了英軍服務團的情報網。1943年4月，日軍登上在澳門的西安號輪船，在船上發現文件，記載了英軍服務團其中一個情報組的資料。日軍由此得知英軍服務團在香港擁有情報網。憲兵隊旋即在市內搜捕英軍服務團人員，<strong>並在5月31日拘捕「M組」首領雷福榮；他隨即自殺，以免被迫供出他人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n結果，華洋軍民被捕者超過二百人，<strong>其中約四十人遭處決，包括紐臨、霍德，以及加利，英軍服務團情報人員包括George Kotewall、劉德愛（雷福榮伴侶）、劉德光（劉德愛兄弟）、李林（戰俘營司機）、曾德、曾耀生兄弟（情報員，其父曾協助與啟德機場的戰俘聯絡）、楊守德（自日本海軍工作部竊取圖則）等</strong>。其餘被捕者則遭受酷刑及囚禁，直至日本投降為止。莫德庇少將曾要求日軍釋放他的官兵，但最終與其他高級戰俘被送到台灣囚禁。//<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.arcgis.com/apps/Cascade/index.html?appid=271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arcgis.com%2Fapps%2FCascade%2Findex.html%3Fappid%3D271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzxxs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=51d04901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.arcgis.com/apps/Cascade/index.html?appid=271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"60a060db69464662e9c9afb21b5cbafe4e02bad7","tid":2344698,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&ldquo;Everybody has to die sometime. Many die daily from disease, some suffer painful, lingering deaths. We will die strong and healthy for an ideal; not as traitors, but nobly in our country&rsquo;s cause. We cannot now escape the enemy&rsquo;s sword, but no one should give in to years or regrets, but instead face the enemy with a smile and die bravely.&rdquo;「人終需一死，很多人因病離世，承受揮之不去的痛楚。我們會堅強而健康地死去，全為信念，不作叛徒，高貴地為國捐軀。我們如今避不過敵人的劍了，但無人應流淚或抱憾，我們要含笑面對敵人，勇敢地命赴黃泉。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b858490cc9cb0cf8e78e48a8474e947484b63d10","tid":2344698,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1942年1月，賴廉士上校（Sir Lindsay Tasman Ride）成功逃出香港後，成立英軍服務團（British Army Aids Group）營救在港戰俘。儘管面對死亡威脅，安薩里仍然按照英軍服務團的指引，秘密與深水埗、亞皆老街戰俘營的英軍軍官聯絡，策劃一場大型逃脫行動。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前守軍就算淪陷後, 都好積極<br />\n<br />\n點以得依家嗰班mk, 去到外國日日食LSD話要chill"},{"pid":"931d1cfd835aee46a6e576123e8a95d4157ccd7f","tid":2344698,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f33ca553712a57ab339dfdfe8de3cc9f70fb004","tid":2344698,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"香港華人唔識咁諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"香港義勇軍都打至最後<br />\n<br />\n有d係淪陷後, 都逃去緬甸入返英軍, 繼續作戰<br />\n<br />\n點似依家班人, 日日係外國唔知做乜, 食LSD, 垃圾"},{"pid":"5103777fcf1c71ec52f1234fa58e4a2d1af68702","tid":2344698,"uid":278085,"like":4,"dis